  "notes": "Philosophy:\nInstant win champs, attack champs in pool directly via Arena.\n\nChampions:\nInstantly win (but are not instantly defeated like Living Scroll and King of the Elves). AD&D for artifacts.  Dragons for Orb of GreenDragonkind.\n\nCombos:\n-Stryck + Wand of Orcus = pick low level defender for auto-win\n-Jacqueline Renier + Whip of Disarming = attack non-spellcaster for auto-win\n-Sword and Helm on Undead Htimsen so any Psionicist that defends is defeated\n-Arena, then attack flyer with Gloriana discards them, or attack undead with Corpse Dragon discards them, or attack a non-cleric, -psionicist, -hero and attack Sword and Helm to discard him also.\n-Corpse Dragon + Arena = kill an undead\nruling here:\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind0412C&L=spellfire-l&P=R1064\nDragon Hatching can kill Dragons by attacking them too.",
